{"id":1173717,"date":[{"year":1998,"month":10,"day":25}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"’98国庆当代诗会作品选","genre":"","count":"157","ytitle":"","mtitle":"望江南(四首)","ftitle":"","authors":["黎明"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南好、最好是春深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通衢杜鹃红似火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风拂杨柳界河荫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留待诗人吟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江好，千古自风流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤壁楼船今安在?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长桥三里跨江头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢缆系巨舟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝钢好，钢厂春意浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉宇琼楼神仙府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁流穿梭绿丛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥看炉火红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华好，赤帜映朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散浮云晴万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州遍开英雄花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新秀振中华。"}]}